    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tools for sweeping. Originally made of twigs fixed to a handle; now refers to handled tools with bristles made of any material.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
